  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients receiving oral anticoagulation or anti-platelet therapy are at high risk of
      hematoma after device implantation.  This study intends to examine the efficacy of the
      TopClosure(c) System in wound healing in these patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
